{"tid":1544524,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"「光復香港」 呢句唔該你每日掛喺嘴邊!!","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T01:05:36.000Z","uid":184233,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c4790ecb9ae150ac9886a2efc9eba5750ef80f9","tid":1544524,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"要將<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></strong></span>呢句變成<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">日常問候語</span></strong></span><br />\n同埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">道謝/Thank You嘅替代品</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7月起每當我去便利店, 餐廳 ... 買野個D時候, 買完野我都會講句 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係所有人都有應我機，但都有不少人係會回我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最感動係返工個到有個看更啊叔，我次次收工都同佢講 光復香港，佢平時都會回我&quot;拜拜&quot;，但831之後，佢有日突然應我機，講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港&amp;時代革命</span></strong></span>唔止係口號同訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">係精神 係信念 <br />\n係文化 係生活</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家都可以養成呢個習慣</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"951431d740c4738f87bf336c1deccc023f21f28a","tid":1544524,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:56:41.000Z","m